c","tid":257582,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T14:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d527eb8cbdb950af98976378e188327cfd8508b","tid":257582,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夠薑燒人大使館<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇嫁佢地只係會燒番中國人開既日本食店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2de49d9f4e9c308b2600cf78dc7ba211c926ec","tid":257582,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"成日掛住抽水 就真係玻璃心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad7be9bde54eeab99833d305881eea808b97dcd","tid":257582,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:00:38.000Z","msg":"如果你話邊個再嘈就掃把佢返中國，啲人就散晒架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cb1c60c7d557eb660f8f523e43006acac70a39","tid":257582,"uid":98477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:32:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強國年青人有極端民族主義唔出奇，細細個就接受紅色教育點會受得住外國批評<br />\n<br />\n<strong>怪就怪在香港土生土長都出現呢種人，見到有D20幾30歲藍屍帶好積極去港人港地、支持香港警察FB page留言，又去鬧爆appledaily，保皇黨仲有班20-30新人正等待上位</strong><br />\n<br />\n都諗唔明佢地成長階段香港都仲未有洗腦教育點解佢地個思想會赤化得咁嚴重<br />\n唔通真係俾陶傑說齋小農DNA果種民族詛咒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲叫商業民族主義，愛國有錢收、有地位就愛國，無錢、無地位就立刻劃清界線。<br />\n羅永生甚至會話呢啲叫勾結式殖民主義。愛國氣節喺香港根本係異類，大部分所謂愛口者都只係以華制華手段下嘅附庸。"},{"pid":"2656700b032b057a8059aaabba231b6ebb51d724","tid":257582,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:36:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>強國年